sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AISystem as AI System
    participant BiasDetector as Bias Detection Service
    participant EthicsFramework as Ethics Framework
    participant AuditLog as Audit Log
    participant GovernanceBoard as Governance Board

    User->>AISystem: Submit request
    activate AISystem
    AISystem->>EthicsFramework: Load ethical rules
    activate EthicsFramework
    EthicsFramework-->>AISystem: Provide constraints
    deactivate EthicsFramework

    AISystem->>AISystem: Generate preliminary decision
    AISystem->>BiasDetector: Analyze decision for bias
    activate BiasDetector
    BiasDetector-->>AISystem: Bias assessment report
    deactivate BiasDetector

    AISystem->>AISystem: Apply constraints and mitigate bias
    AISystem->>AuditLog: Record decision rationale and bias report
    activate AuditLog
    AuditLog-->>AISystem: Logged
    deactivate AuditLog

    AISystem-->>User: Provide transparent decision + explanation
    AISystem->>GovernanceBoard: Submit governance report
    activate GovernanceBoard
    GovernanceBoard-->>AISystem: Acknowledge
    deactivate GovernanceBoard
    deactivate AISystem